name: Perform evaluation on a preconfigured inference unit without essential evaluation criteria

steps.name: Given a valid, preconfigured inference unit for image multilabel classification
And an evaluation plan with no criteria for image multilabel classification
When we run inference unit evaluation
Then a successful result indicating all criteria passed is computed
Then the precision metric for class name Adventure is calculated to be 0.6
Then the recall metric for class name Comedy is calculated to be 0.62
Then the f1 metric for class name Drama is calculated to be 0.51
Then the rocauc metric for class name Romance is calculated to be 0.79
Then the acc metric for class name Sci-Fi is calculated to be 0.86
